<hr />

<p>낮은 지수 공격이다.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="n">Crypto.Util.number</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="o">*</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="n">gmpy2</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="o">*</span>

<span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi"></span>
<span class="n">e</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">3</span>
<span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">2449457955338174702664398437699732241330055959255401949300755756893329242892325068765174475595370736008843435168081093064803408113260941928784442707977000585466461075146434876354981528996602615111767938231799146073229307631775810351487333</span>

<span class="k">with</span> <span class="nf">local_context</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">lcx</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">lcx</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">precision</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">1000</span>
    <span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nf">long_to_bytes</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nf">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nf">root</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">e</span><span class="p">))))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Solution]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">ezdlp</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/ezdlp/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="ezdlp" /><published>2023-05-27T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-27T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/ezdlp</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/ezdlp/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="background">Background</h2>
<hr />

<blockquote>
  <p>one easy dlp</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">g</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">8999</span> 
<span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">11721478752747238947534577901795278971298347908127389421908790123</span> 
<span class="n">p</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi"></span>

<span class="n">g</span><span class="o">^</span><span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">s</span> <span class="n">mod</span> <span class="n">p</span>
<span class="n">flag</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">tjctf</span><span class="p">{</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">}</span>

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>\(g^X = s \bmod p\) 에서 x를 구하면 된다.</p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />

<p>sage를 사용한다. sage에는 이산로그 문제를 푸는 함수가 존재한다.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">g</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">8999</span>
<span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">11721478752747238947534577901795278971298347908127389421908790123</span>
<span class="n">p</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi"></span>

<span class="n">Fp</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nc">IntegerModRing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">p</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">g_modp</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nc">Fp</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">g</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">s_modp</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nc">Fp</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">x</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nf">discrete_log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s_modp</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">g_modp</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="nf">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="s">The value of x is:</span><span class="sh">"</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">he value of x is: 26104478854569770948763268629079094351020764258425704346666185171631094713742516526074910325202612575130356252792856014835908436517926646322189289728462011794148513926930343382081388714077889318297349665740061482743137948635476088264751212120906948450722431680198753238856720828205708702161666784517</code></p>

<p>ㅎ ㅏ sage 쓰는 법을 몰라서 못풀었다.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Background]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">006 serises</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/006series/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="006 serises" /><published>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/006series</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/006series/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="background">Background</h2>
