<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/30267e82-570c-46d7-83bf-fb749ca81926" alt="Untitled (8)" /></p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />
<p>3개의 문제로 되어있고, 각 문제 파일에는 특정 알고리즘으로 hash화 된 암호가 있다.</p>

<p><a href="https://crackstation.net/">CrackStation - Online Password Hash Cracking - MD5, SHA1, Linux, Rainbow Tables, etc.</a></p>

<p>이 사이트에 넣으면 대부분 나오고</p>

<p>안나오는 암호는</p>

<p><a href="https://hashes.com/en/decrypt/hash">Decrypt MD5, SHA1, MySQL, NTLM, SHA256, SHA512, Wordpress, Bcrypt hashes for free online</a></p>

<p>여기에 넣으면 나왔다.</p>

<p>md5, sha256, sha512 알고리즘이 사용되었다.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Background]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">BYUCTF 2023 12nd</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/BYUCTF-2023/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="BYUCTF 2023 12nd" /><published>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/BYUCTF%202023</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/BYUCTF-2023/"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://ctftime.org/media/events/_97185d4c-8460-47e4-9498-cb0e8a4e2f0e.jpg" alt="image" width="60%" height="100%" /></p>

