<hr />

<blockquote>
  <p>Apparently this is meant to replace the Latin alphabet??</p>

  <p>Flag format: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">byuctf{word or phrase}</code> case insensitve.</p>

</blockquote>

<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/aa79b8b0-0a53-4e80-9676-1d39ee118b61" alt="Untitled" width="100%" height="100%" /></p>

<p>이 이미지에서 단어를 찾아내어야 한다.</p>

<p>모스 부호와 관련있어보이긴 했어서 무작정 검색했었다.</p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/69e15a00-7098-4906-83f9-564da23858ca" alt="Untitled" width="100%" height="100%" /></p>

<p>그랬더니 이 표가 보인다.</p>

<p>왼쪽 박스 부분이 연관있어보이긴 하는데, 제목과도 합치면 이 박스가 Compact 되어있는 것 같다.</p>

<p>이걸 어떻게 해석하지?</p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />

<p>계속.. 찾아다니고 이것저것 숫자를 넣어보고  <a href="https://www.dcode.fr/baudot-code">https://www.dcode.fr/baudot-code</a> 이것도 보고 그랬는데</p>

<p>결과적으로 <a href="https://www.dcode.fr/symbols-ciphers">https://www.dcode.fr/symbols-ciphers</a> 을 찾아보다가 dotsies cipher와 유사해보였다. 디코딩을 하니까</p>

<p><a href="https://www.dcode.fr/symbols-ciphers">https://www.dcode.fr/symbols-ciphers</a></p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/94b03cce-96eb-45e2-b3d3-ab40d1cf90ac" alt="Untitled" width="100%" height="100%" /></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">byuctf{well its definitely more compact}</code></p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Background]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">𐐗𐐡𐐆𐐑𐐓𐐄?</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/deseret/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="𐐗𐐡𐐆𐐑𐐓𐐄?" /><published>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/deseret</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/deseret/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="background">Background</h2>
<hr />

<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/de52a73b-a134-4a2c-bf9f-19daa8abc29e" alt="Untitled" width="100%" height="100%" /></p>

<p>별 말 없이 사진만 던져짐</p>

<p>제목을 검색하니 문자가 데저릿 문자라는걸 알겠음</p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />

<p><a href="https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EB%8D%B0%EC%A0%80%EB%A0%9B_%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90">https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/데저렛_문자</a></p>

<p>데저릿을 번역하는 사이트</p>

<p><img src="https://github.com/neutrinox4b1/neutrinox4b1.github.io/assets/101745344/50d183f7-8188-4e9a-b9fb-636c85eea6c9" alt="Untitled" width="100%" height="100%" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.2deseret.com/">https://www.2deseret.com/</a></p>

<p>앞에 저 부분이 ㅋㅋ 읽어보니 byuctf</p>

<p>근데 뒤에 해석되지 않는 부분은 발음과 비슷한 걸 검색해서 찾음</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">byuctf{deseret_means_honeybee}</code></p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Background]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Poem</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/poem/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Poem" /><published>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/poem</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/poem/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="background">Background</h2>
<hr />

<blockquote>
  <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">epcndkohlxfgvenkzcllkoclivdckskvpkddcyoceipkvrcslkdhycbcscwcsc</code></p>

  <p>Spaces and punctuation were removed :)</p>

  <p>Flag format - <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">byuctf{the phrase goes here}</code> note there are spaces in the flag, no other punctuation needed.</p>

</blockquote>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">epcndkohlxfgvenkzcllkoclivdckskvpkddcyoceipkvrcslkdhycbcscwcsc</code></p>

<p>아니 이게 암호문임</p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />
<p><a href="https://www.dcode.fr/keyboard-change-cipher">Keyboard Change Cipher - Online QWERTY Shifter/Converter (dcode.fr)</a></p>

<p>thefragisbyuctf a message so crealacharrengetohackelsarinewe levele</p>

<p>l ↔ r 바꾸면</p>

<p>the flag is byuctf a message so clear a challenge to hackers a line we revere</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="crypto" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Background]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">RSA1</title><link href="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/rsa1/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="RSA1" /><published>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2023-05-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/rsa1</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://neutrinox4b1.github.io/blog/2023/rsa1/"><![CDATA[<h2 id="background">Background</h2>
<hr />

<blockquote>
  <p>n = 287838647563564518717519107521814079281</p>

  <p>e = 7</p>

  <p>c = 258476617615202392748150555415953446503</p>

</blockquote>

<p>287838647563564518717519107521814079281 = 15631612382272805561 * 18413880828441662521</p>

<p><br />
<br />
<br /></p>

<h2 id="solution">Solution</h2>
<hr />

<p>n 값이 소인수분해 가능하게 작음</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="n">Crypto.Util.number</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="o">*</span>

